## Client-side data processing

This part of the lib provides an API to dynamically interact with iterable data on the client-side: filtering, paging, sorting, selectingâ€¦

- **Headless** by design
- **Typescript** support
- **SSR** friendly
- no dependencies

Also provides some demo components, which you can grab and customize in your own project.

## Sample code

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
    import { DataHandler } from '@vincjo/datatables'
    import { someData } from './data'

    const handler = new DataHandler(someData, { rowsPerPage: 50 })
    const rows = handler.getRows()
</script>

<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>First name</th>
            <th>Last name</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {#each $rows as row}
            <tr>
                <td>{row.first_name}</td>
                <td>{row.last_name}</td>
            </tr>
        {/each}
    </tbody>
</table>
```
